"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-paris-stabbing-soldier-gare-de-lest-olympics-france-security-b1170892.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World  AFrench soldierwas stabbed outside a train station inParis, just 11 days before the city hosts the 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The soldier was rushed to hospital with a shoulder blade injury after being attacked while on patrol at the Gare de l'Est train station in easternParison Monday.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The attacker was arrested and French officials confirmed the soldier was not in life-threatening condition.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9976811488641767, \"rank\": 0.0022497536006326935, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The motive for theattackwas under investigation, the Paris prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2353281566625254e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An investigation was opened into attempted murder, and the suspect's identity was being confirmed, the prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities did not suspect terrorism as a motive at this stage, according to the national counterterrorism prosecutor's office.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is under a highsecurityalert ahead of theOlympics, with the opening ceremony taking place on July 26.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2353281566625254e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The soldier was among thousands of troops serving in the Sentinelle force forFrance's domestic security, created to guard prominent French sites after a string of deadly Islamic extremist attacks in 2015.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9976811488641767, \"rank\": 0.0022497536006326935, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Islamic extremist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soldiers in the Sentinelle force have been targeted in the past.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin posted on X that the soldier was patrolling at the Gare de l'Est train station in eastern Paris, and that the assailant was detained.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 0.998670871982765, \"rank\": 0.0013108350459732924, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\"}, {\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9982503864259639, \"rank\": 0.0017518689605769582, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2353281566625254e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is deploying around 30,000 police officers each day for the Olympics, which run from July 26 to August 11, with a peak of 45,000 for the opening ceremony on the Seine river.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2353281566625254e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1689, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia